{
  "id": "019d286c-c8e3-7462-a4e5-a2e4efbe5bc3",
  "content": "\">Don't Tell You</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 36px;\">\n    A benchmark is only as honest as its caveats. Here are the things I'd want to know\n    before drawing conclusions from these numbers.\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; flex: 1;\">\n    <!-- Caveat 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#9888;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px;\">CPU short-text anomaly is <span class=\"highlight-red\">misleading</span></div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65;\">\n          527ms looks terrible, but it's ORT's batch startup cost spread over only 5 items.\n          With 10+ items, CPU drops to 56ms/embed — nearly matching GPU backends.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>\n\n    <!-- Caveat 2 -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 32px; flex-shrink: 0;\">&#128203;</div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Pipeline overhead <span class=\"highlight\">dominates</span></div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65;\">\n          ~45-50ms of every request is CLI + HTTP + gRPC + HNSW search. Pure inference\n          time is only ~5-10ms on GPU. The backend matters less than you'd think.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"divider\" style=\"margin: 0;\"></div>",
